column5: Gonna try my luck at the Toronto Islands for some pike tomorrow... just wondering if anyone else is heading out tomorrow. If you are, I'll be there around 8-9... i'll have my red ny firemens cap with me  hope to see u out there!
i might be down there some time in the early afternoon.  hmm. i'll be the guy with a fishing pole. hehe  see ya out there, good luck
